  ${
    $d f A $.  $d f B $.
    mapval.1 $e |- A e. V $.
    mapval.2 $e |- B e. V $.
    $( The value of set exponentiation (inference version).  ` ( A ^m B ) `
       is the set of all functions that map from ` B ` to ` A ` .  Definition
       10.24 of [Kunen] p. 24. $)
    mapval $p |-  ( A ^m B ) = { f | f : B --> A } $=
